source_description:
GUCCI
Python  Jackie Large Top Handle Bag
We can always count on Gucci for styles that we will love now and later. This lovely   Gucci brown python  Leather Soft Jackie Large Top Handle Bag features python leather and gold Gucci piston push-lock closure. The bag has two rolled  top handles and a  roomy interior is perfect for holding all your daily essentials in style
Measurements: 16.5" L x 5.5"W x 12" H
Interior Pockets: Two zip pockets
Handles: Double rolled leather handles
Handle Drop: 5"
Closure/Opening: Open top with piston push-lock
Interior Lining: Unlined leather
product_title: Gucci Top Handle Bag Jackie Large Brown Python Tote
